Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.09,0:01:44.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Continuing from last episode, we're still at Yumesaki High's Cultural Festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.84,0:01:48.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This place is especially crowded; let's go somewhere else.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.79,0:01:50.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A-Alright...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.94,0:01:53.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I came here because I was worried about Sakura.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.43,0:01:57.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We got separated, but it'll be pointless if I go back now.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.87,0:02:00.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe someone from our school is here as well!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.06,0:02:01.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess so...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.10,0:02:04.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I'll kill time with Usui 'til the live performance is over.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.98,0:02:06.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The grilled squid was delicious! {Hmm, I'm not sure if grill is the right one; I'm guessing it's skewered squids burned over fire}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.30,0:02:07.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.03,0:02:08.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What shall we try next?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.01,0:02:08.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The fried stuff!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.76,0:02:10.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,OK! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.95,0:02:12.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's really crowded here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.97,0:02:14.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.96,0:02:18.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How did you manage to get all those?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.58,0:02:20.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For some reason, the passersby gave them to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.46,0:02:22.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They told me to try them out. {well, 'food sampling' is the lit}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.58,0:02:24.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean by 'some reason'?! That's weird!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.75,0:02:26.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe it's {\i1}that{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.25,0:02:28.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I made {\i1}their{\i0} flowers bloom. {This line is horrible; I'm guessing it's a figurative speech, and < is a direct TL, so doesn't make much sense. Well, I think it's something to do with girls being attracted to handsome guy, so do a liberal edit as fit}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.01,0:02:30.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn, I'm getting surrounded again. Let's run!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.60,0:02:37.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where is that hot guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.53,0:02:38.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.35,0:02:40.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know what's happening, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.21,0:02:45.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't make their flowers bloom again. What kind of magic did you pull? {Ok, don't think trickery is the right word, guess she's referring to the stuff Usui has now}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.42,0:02:47.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think that's the right word... {referring to her usage of 'magic'}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.35,0:02:48.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the point of doing that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.18,0:02:50.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uhh... to spark off jealousy?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.97,0:02:52.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Between who?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.15,0:02:56.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, cool down. Why not try some food here?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.32,0:02:58.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm fine. I'm not really hungry...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.78,0:02:59.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.13,0:03:03.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's rather tasty.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.63,0:03:10.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.18,0:03:14.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.00,0:03:18.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This feels strange... It's just like...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.06,0:03:20.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...a date, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.06,0:03:21.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks good on you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.22,0:03:24.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you read into my mind again?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.77,0:03:28.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You perverted alien! What's with that superhuman power?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.62,0:03:32.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just what exactly are you?! {Ok, powers here refers to peeking into other's minds, and the making flowers bloom part}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.41,0:03:35.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Why are you laughing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.21,0:03:37.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry. Ayuzawa...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.99,0:03:40.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're thinking of the same things as I am, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.09,0:03:46.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.88,0:03:50.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A-Anywhere! I can't be sitting here idly in a festival!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.94,0:03:51.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.84,0:03:58.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I tried most of the food here already.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.09,0:03:58.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Same here!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.95,0:04:01.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's try out the events next!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.49,0:04:01.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this 'Old Mansion' thingy?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.72,0:04:04.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see how 'ancient' the designs are!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.27,0:04:04.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.48,0:04:07.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you win the game console that you wanted?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.27,0:04:09.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won it with only a single postcard!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.20,0:04:10.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.11,0:04:12.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no lucky draw club here, I guess. {ok, still strange, she's referring to her... 'oddball' club where they send out postcards for lucky draw contest. you can check earlier scripts, I rmbr I encountered this before, not sure what ep though.}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.00,0:04:12.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It {\i1}is{\i0} an unusual club, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.98,0:04:14.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's eat some steamed buns. {ok, possibly contradicting TL. Steamed buns is what you normally translate manjuu to, and yaki is fried, so combining both = yaki manjuu. Google 焼き饅頭 for pics to reference}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.30,0:04:16.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kanou, let's get some fried stuff!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.16,0:04:17.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.70,0:04:19.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Froggy~
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.66,0:04:20.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Mr. Froggy~
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.74,0:04:23.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn, I'm still feeling hot.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.34,0:04:26.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've got an event just right for the both of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.50,0:04:28.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Try our "Love Trial"!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.09,0:04:30.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Test out the strength of your relationship!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.46,0:04:32.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're not a couple-
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.63,0:04:33.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The rule is simple:
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.80,0:04:38.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Follow the designated course and clear the challenges along the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.92,0:04:41.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll be eliminated if you fail even once!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.21,0:04:43.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you manage to succeed, the prize is this:
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.37,0:04:47.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A super premium ticket to the post-festival event!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.21,0:04:48.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Woah! Amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.65,0:04:48.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.44,0:04:51.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You mustn't let go of your partner's hand during the game.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.65,0:04:55.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well then, will you be able to overcome the trials ahead together?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.03,0:04:57.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dare to take up the challenge?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.75,0:04:58.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.39,0:05:00.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey you-
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.43,0:05:06.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to see for myself if a romance between us is really impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.66,0:05:09.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A romance between the two of you cannot happen.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.75,0:05:12.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're still thinking about that-
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.13,0:05:15.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's face this obstacle together, 'kay?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.34,0:05:17.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for participating!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.53,0:05:21.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez, this is such a waste of money.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.43,0:05:25.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can enjoy a lot of things just for 500 yen! It's a bargain, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.76,0:05:26.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe, but still...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.86,0:05:28.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah, take off your ribbon.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.81,0:05:32.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the proof of participation and it has to be kept visible at all times.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.61,0:05:34.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm supposed to wear that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.29,0:05:36.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it looks good on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.86,0:05:43.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They say it's fine to bring it back with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.37,0:05:46.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not such a waste after all, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.37,0:05:50.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine to enjoy yourself once in a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.40,0:05:54.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll get that frown embedded on your face if you always have it on.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.05,0:05:56.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shall we go?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.04,0:05:57.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.05,0:05:59.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.95,0:05:59.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.70,0:06:03.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You hate me, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.70,0:06:11.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not for you to say, idiot. {awk, consider liberal}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.06,0:06:15.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can we go back now?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.19,0:06:16.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shizuko!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.55,0:06:20.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next up is Kamiyama and Oono's comedic skit.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.59,0:06:21.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kamiyama here!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.53,0:06:22.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Oono.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.30,0:06:27.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're the comedic duo! {ok, hanging sentence again, lit is just "we're the - "}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.13,0:06:27.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's boring!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.62,0:06:29.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that supposed to be my fault?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.41,0:06:31.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When will UxMishi come out?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.97,0:06:33.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, 2 hours later?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.46,0:06:35.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have 2 hours to lecture you then.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.96,0:06:37.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shizuko...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.28,0:06:40.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you willing to wait so long for this?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.65,0:06:45.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd rather be with Misaki and go back first.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.83,0:06:47.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.89,0:06:51.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with this course of events?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.34,0:06:55.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why am I holding hands with Usui in this game?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.44,0:06:56.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just like a date, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.15,0:07:02.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not! I'm supposed to be with Sakura and Shizuko!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.08,0:07:03.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How did it turn out like this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.20,0:07:04.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.81,0:07:06.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your Love Trial starts now!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.91,0:07:10.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong? We have to clear this within 10 minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.04,0:07:12.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't hinder me, Prez.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.66,0:07:15.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who will?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.92,0:07:19.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your face is pissing me off! {face referring to that face usui put on when challenging her}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.33,0:07:22.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You aren't supposed to run on the corridors, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.79,0:07:24.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up! I'm just walking quickly!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.05,0:07:24.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This{\i0} is walking quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.87,0:07:26.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That looks creepy! {referring to usui's fast-walk}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.68,0:07:29.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm surprised we didn't meet anyone we know.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.76,0:07:31.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.00,0:07:33.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this sound I'm hearing...?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.02,0:07:34.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here, this is my proof of participation.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.01,0:07:36.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Man, we took 3 minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.15,0:07:38.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd have taken only a minute to get here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.42,0:07:41.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell? I'd have done it in 30 seconds!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.61,0:07:44.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please explain the game to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.99,0:07:44.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.03,0:07:48.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Finish this within 10 minutes!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.49,0:07:50.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be simple for two people.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.50,0:07:52.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Only one of you will do the eating.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.54,0:07:54.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm feeling some hostility from behind...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.46,0:07:56.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The other couples barely cleared this stage!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.69,0:07:58.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good luck, for the sake of your girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.29,0:07:59.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's decide using rock, paper, scissors.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.54,0:08:02.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What, you think that I'm unable to finish this?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.55,0:08:04.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Why would I? Let's get this on.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.17,0:08:06.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rock, paper, scissors!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.55,0:08:09.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fine, I'll finish everything right to the last drop of soup!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.18,0:08:12.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh...?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.02,0:08:14.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, can I let go of his hand for this game?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.09,0:08:15.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll be disqualified.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.22,0:08:17.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll have to eat with my left then.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.83,0:08:20.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is where I come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.82,0:08:23.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll feed you, so just enjoy the food.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.32,0:08:25.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no need! I'll manage this alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.50,0:08:26.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please signal the start.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.52,0:08:28.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright, ready, go!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.20,0:08:30.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ramen, ramen, for your man! {my liberal one here, this is just some cutesy shit}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.58,0:08:31.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The game starts now!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.66,0:08:33.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here, ahh~
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.33,0:08:38.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up, or you won't be able to finish within 10 minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.08,0:08:39.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the girl who's doing the eating!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.39,0:08:40.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do your best!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.02,0:08:41.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Want me to blow on it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.21,0:08:43.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! It's fine as it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.68,0:08:46.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be just what he wants if I feel embarrassed here!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.54,0:08:51.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You suck, Prez. Come on, it's here~
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.76,0:08:56.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here, come take it~
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.76,0:08:56.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{Drop, or I'll TL this as > RaaaaaaAAAAAAAGE!}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.64,0:08:58.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, it's getting crazy over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.80,0:09:01.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You mean Class 3-1's ramen house? That extra large servings challenge?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.81,0:09:05.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! A couple's duking it out at godly speed!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.99,0:09:08.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, that couple did something amazing again!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.51,0:09:10.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The next game was Class 3-2's card game, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.45,0:09:13.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Toran, who was unbeatable in speed games,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.04,0:09:15.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lost to them at the speed of light!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.79,0:09:19.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're devils! Devils, I tell you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.29,0:09:20.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It got even crazier next!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.96,0:09:22.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,3-3's doing table tennis, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.60,0:09:26.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Usually it'll be hard to win using the hand you're not used to. {ok, can't remember the phrase for this}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.11,0:09:27.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the-?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.97,0:09:30.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's not a left-hander?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.66,0:09:33.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've won, but I can't seem to control my strength...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.60,0:09:35.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Trying to give an excuse since you're naturally a right-hander?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.38,0:09:38.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! I'm just not in top form!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.02,0:09:41.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're no ordinary couple!  They're...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.69,0:09:44.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...a superhuman tag team!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.11,0:09:46.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome to the balloon quiz!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.32,0:09:49.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,First, find a balloon marked with the word "Lucky". {Ok, atari doesn't really mean lucky, literally means hit}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.11,0:09:52.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, burst it, and answer the questions on the paper that's inside it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.22,0:09:55.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There! It's those two!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.86,0:09:55.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have 5 minutes. Start!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.39,0:09:57.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're attracting quite a lot of attention...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.61,0:09:59.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We stood out too much, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.87,0:10:02.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe it's about time to tell her straight...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.59,0:10:03.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.59,0:10:04.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.84,0:10:07.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's race to see who finds the balloon first.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.83,0:10:09.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Interesting. I'll take you on!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.83,0:10:14.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See? I found it...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.72,0:10:18.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...already...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.68,0:10:23.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you spacing out? There's a time limit, you know?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.02,0:10:24.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed. {hmm, this is the accurate TL, but flow is horrible. I'd go with "Sorry", but is a totally different TL altogether...}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.27,0:10:29.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's burst it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.74,0:10:32.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sakura, listen.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.62,0:10:34.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm against him from the start.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.28,0:10:37.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's arrogant, and his looks are outrageous as well. {referring to kuuga's outwar appearance, so maybe an edit needed}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.87,0:10:40.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just what do you see in him?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.12,0:10:43.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm getting more and more annoyed waiting in this crowd!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.64,0:10:45.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shizuko...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.07,0:10:47.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, I got loud there.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.96,0:10:50.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shizuko's getting unstable...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.38,0:10:52.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I should've put it in a nicer way.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.67,0:10:54.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm really sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.78,0:10:57.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't explain it well, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.35,0:11:03.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, let's see...  He's cool, and I admire him for how he chases after his dreams.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.96,0:11:09.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But that's not all. I just can't describe it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.19,0:11:13.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The feeling of 'love' overflows from somewhere else.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.93,0:11:18.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if people are against it and you know you can't make the cut,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.43,0:11:23.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,once you realize this feeling, it's unstoppable.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.83,0:11:27.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've cleared it superbly! Congratulations!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.59,0:11:31.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a special invitation for tonight's post-festival event.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.08,0:11:33.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please enjoy it to the end!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.02,0:11:34.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How nice...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.05,0:11:37.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why is Misa-chan taking the day off?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.06,0:11:39.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No idea... Don't ask me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.02,0:11:40.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She has something on?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.98,0:11:43.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She should have asked me to go along with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.47,0:11:45.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way that'll happen, you perv.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.69,0:11:49.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My, my, I see you're relaxing comfortably here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.27,0:11:50.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, to the point of becoming blobs. {alright, liberal one here. What they wanted to say is that they've relaxed so much that they've... melted down? lol}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.69,0:11:52.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't distinguish between us now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.57,0:11:54.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We aren't even humans anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.55,0:11:58.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad that you're relaxing that much over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.05,0:11:59.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please take your time and enjoy yourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.70,0:12:00.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay~
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.73,0:12:03.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for waiting. Here is your cream soda.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.55,0:12:04.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yay~!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.60,0:12:06.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's here!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.79,0:12:08.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry for being late, Manager.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.87,0:12:11.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Me too, I had some unfinished business to attend to.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.72,0:12:14.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine, I'm glad you both came to help.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.51,0:12:15.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, how are we going to drink this?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.80,0:12:17.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't drink in this form...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.68,0:12:19.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How do we transform back?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.89,0:12:23.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, it was rather fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.42,0:12:26.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You were having fun teasing me, weren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.23,0:12:28.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Was I the only one having fun?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.77,0:12:30.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.82,0:12:32.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I had fun as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.78,0:12:37.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go retrieve your bag.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.62,0:13:28.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It started!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.58,0:13:30.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seems like it started.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.22,0:13:32.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It got delayed quite a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.42,0:13:33.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How did you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.54,0:13:34.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's written here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.95,0:14:00.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The nearer it is to the stage, the more crowded it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.57,0:14:03.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why we should meet up with them after it ends.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.48,0:14:06.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought it'd be better to get closer to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.57,0:14:09.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Usu-
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.78,0:14:14.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you alright? Could it be that you almost got separated from me?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.70,0:14:17.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you want to hold my hand, just like before?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.62,0:14:20.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.91,0:14:52.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's gripping me tightly!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.15,0:15:22.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello, Sakura?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.58,0:15:24.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The live ended already, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.79,0:15:26.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? You can't meet up with us?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.50,0:15:33.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez, I'll do the explaining!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.04,0:15:37.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to stroll around the festival grounds with UxMishi.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.25,0:15:39.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? UxMishi?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.20,0:15:45.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez, I thought some girls chased after me again.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.68,0:15:47.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kuuga called just now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.87,0:15:52.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They wanted to take a look around without being noticed, so they asked us along.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.65,0:15:53.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see... Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.94,0:15:56.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll call you back later.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.37,0:15:59.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, glaring at me like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.76,0:16:02.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry, I'm not the least bit interested in you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.59,0:16:06.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to get scolded like that again.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.86,0:16:08.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is your intention?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.14,0:16:10.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,About what? Sakura?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.08,0:16:12.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it wrong for me to invite her for a stroll?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.45,0:16:16.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know she wouldn't refuse, so you're just using her, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.25,0:16:17.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're scary, as usual.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.92,0:16:20.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To tell you the truth, I don't trust you at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.57,0:16:27.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But Sakura told me you've changed, so I came here to see for myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.17,0:16:29.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Changed... eh....
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.97,0:16:33.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop using that glare on me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.62,0:16:35.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, but this is just how I look.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.26,0:16:38.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm staring hard to spot where you might have changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.44,0:16:40.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You won't get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.58,0:16:42.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kuuga, I brought these for you today!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.96,0:16:46.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's the only one who sees me for who I am. {'look' here is figurative, might mean to consider someone seriously as a partner}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.66,0:16:49.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're serious about Sakura-
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.70,0:16:50.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.74,0:16:52.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're being overprotective!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.74,0:16:56.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just go play along with your boyfriend and leave us alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.04,0:16:56.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Boyfriend?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.75,0:16:58.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That stalker guy you mentioned.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.91,0:17:02.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,N-No! He's just a perverted alien stalker!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.30,0:17:06.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, don't tell me he's still enduring it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.05,0:17:06.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you-
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.91,0:17:10.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not only clueless, but strict and violent as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.69,0:17:12.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd ditch you already if I were him.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.93,0:17:15.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn't want to be with you either!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.09,0:17:17.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How scary~  Catch ya later~
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.23,0:17:22.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did he mean by 'enduring'?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.03,0:17:24.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry for the wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.45,0:17:27.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was packed with people, so I had to wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.15,0:17:30.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.00,0:17:32.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-It's nothing...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.67,0:17:38.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I've completed what I came here to do... I think. {that is, to see kuuga with her own eyes}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.91,0:17:41.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh, you're not acting like your usual self.{out of form? not her usual self? something along that line I guess}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.72,0:17:45.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not up to me to decide anyway. {referring to Shizuko x Kuuga I think}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.17,0:17:49.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, since we're done already, shall we head back?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.35,0:17:53.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Wait! Since we're here already...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.27,0:17:55.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanna stay on til' it ends...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.01,0:17:58.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Usui, are you still free?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.59,0:18:02.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is very unexpected indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.90,0:18:06.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?! I just felt like inviting you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.23,0:18:07.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fine! I'll just go there alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.45,0:18:08.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.86,0:18:12.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We cleared the trial and got this special invitation anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.76,0:18:19.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So this is what they meant by {\i1}special service{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.46,0:18:21.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You look perfect in that!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.58,0:18:24.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Create your own special memories in this special uniform on this special night!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.85,0:18:27.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please enjoy yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.30,0:18:29.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Romeo's waiting for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.80,0:18:33.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.76,0:18:36.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You look good, Juliet.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.95,0:18:36.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it! It's embarrassing!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.51,0:18:39.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Heard they're going to have fireworks in this event.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.08,0:18:40.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.07,0:18:41.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since we're here already, let's watch that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.89,0:18:42.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.83,0:18:47.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good, this place seems to have the best view of the fireworks.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.19,0:18:48.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it fine to enter just like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.57,0:18:51.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine as long as we don't mess it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.78,0:18:54.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.45,0:18:56.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Ayuzawa?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.82,0:18:59.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,N-Nothing's w-wrong...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.07,0:19:01.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it? Fine then.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.16,0:19:05.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's change places. Watching it from the campfire site might be better.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.37,0:19:07.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A-Are you enduring this?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.25,0:19:08.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You mean the fireworks? Not really-  {ok, a bitch here, gaman to put it plainly is just tahan(malay, strangely fits the TL better), usui thought misaki meant waiting for the fireworks to start, so edit the word accordingly. Also, check earlier lines, Kuuga's gaman saseru part}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.80,0:19:10.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not what I meant...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.45,0:19:14.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you... enduring a lot of things just for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.50,0:19:17.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.85,0:19:21.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I... just felt that way...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.94,0:19:23.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ehh... So you knew about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.26,0:19:25.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I was right? What were you- {enduring through}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.37,0:19:26.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How cruel of you, Ayuzawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.98,0:19:29.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you want me to say it out?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.32,0:19:35.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll tell you if you answer my question.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.37,0:19:36.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.22,0:19:38.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you that bothered by me?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.70,0:19:41.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no reason-
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.37,0:19:44.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know it myself, even if you ask me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.71,0:19:46.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't know, eh...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.71,0:19:49.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.71,0:19:52.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You always lie at times like this. {Coz she's a fucking tsundere. FUCKING TSUNDERE, I TELL YOU!! WAIT LONG LONG IF YOU WANNA HEAR THE 3 WORDS!!}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.69,0:19:54.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What are you saying?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.98,0:19:57.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you blushing so hard now?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.31,0:19:58.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not blushing-!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.70,0:19:59.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you nervous?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.57,0:20:01.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm... I'm not!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.92,0:20:05.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you enduring as well?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.23,0:20:11.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, I crossed the line.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.06,0:20:13.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.78,0:20:17.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been enduring!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.74,0:20:21.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why must it be you?! I don't get it at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.46,0:20:23.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're a pervert who annoys me all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.00,0:20:26.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're always running ahead of me and teasing me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.85,0:20:26.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ayuzawa!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.46,0:20:27.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's your fault!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.37,0:20:30.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Calm down!  What are you saying-
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.87,0:20:30.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn't have realized it if not for that game!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.46,0:20:33.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to join hands with you since a long time ago! {THAT'S IT? THAT'S FUCKING IT?! OH FUCK YOU, how long are you gonna drag this shit?!}{Someone's jealous~}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.34,0:20:39.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One moment you're sexually harassing me, and then gone the next...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.01,0:20:41.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just what are you thinking?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.60,0:20:44.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why is my heart beating so fast?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.39,0:20:47.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do I feel lonely when you leave me? {Oh, welcome to enlightenment 101}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.76,0:20:50.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.32,0:20:54.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...the only one causing me so much confusion?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.11,0:20:58.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You idiot, why do you always tease me?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.51,0:21:03.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're really sly, Ayuzawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.62,0:21:06.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just how much more are you gonna make me endure?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.96,0:21:12.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to see your interesting expressions, that's why I teased you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.04,0:21:16.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your sudden smiles always surprise me. {ok, what he's saying here is that her sudden unexpected smiles, out of her usual strict demenour}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.55,0:21:19.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're interesting, but dangerous {ok, dangerous in the sense when nadeko goes "Oniichan, dame?" and looks at you with the eyes. THE EYES, OH SH-}enough to make my heart race.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.11,0:21:26.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have been enduring a lot of things, and I can't phrase it short.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.01,0:21:29.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even now...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.15,0:21:58.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is what's on my mind right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.26,0:22:03.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I love you, Ayuzawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.32,0:22:09.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.43,0:22:10.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,... hate you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.08,0:22:14.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're really sly, Ayuzawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.21,0:22:17.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Usui, you idiot...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.70,0:23:11.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I forgot we need aprons for today's lesson!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.49,0:23:13.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.67,0:23:16.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here's an apron I won from a postcard draw! {hmm, I'm not too sure how this work, kinda like a lucky draw where the winning postcard is drawn.}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.04,0:23:18.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone will be happy if you wear this!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.04,0:23:18.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who will?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.75,0:23:21.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder who~
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.50,0:23:28.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the quiet tea time before opening hours~
